Young Kurdish girl claims she is firing machine gun at 'Daesh', the Arabic name for ISIS . 
  She tells a man she is 'shooting at Daesh' in Kurdish and tells him she has killed 400 of the extremists so far . 
  She is egged on with cries of 'kill, kill' as she fires rounds into the desert . 
  ISIS is known to use children as fighters and executioners . 
  Kurds are famous for their female fighters and have been key in the fight against ISIS . 
 